News.Title: Jay Bee Laminations Secures ₹172.63 Crore Contracts from ABI Energy Solutions
News.Summary: Jay Bee Laminations has received two contracts worth ₹172.63 crores from ABI Energy Solutions for plant supply and installation services in Punjab. The project is scheduled to be completed within 24 months.

News.Title: Jay Bee Laminations Wins ₹94.86 Crore EPC Contract for Haryana Transmission Lines
News.Summary: Jay Bee Laminations has secured a ₹94.86 crore EPC contract from ABI Energy Solutions for transmission lines in Haryana. The company expects this contract to increase its annual revenue by approximately 30% over the next 12 months.

News.Title: Jay Bee Laminations Signs Agreement With Abi Energy For EPC Projects
News.Summary: Jay Bee Laminations has entered into an agreement with Abi Energy for EPC (Engineering, Procurement, and Construction) projects.
